   - Following up: Intrigued by mention of sun-dried opossum,
 &UR; Jere Holbrook  &LR; checked out its food values and found the meat
contains a mere 221 calories per 31/2-ounce serving. Even healthier
is muskrat: only 153 calories per same-size serving. And  &UR; John
Kraft  &LR; has found another use for those free CDs from AOL: to
separate frozen hamburger patties.
